{"tid":209793,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"關於牛涮X問題","createTime":"2017-04-20T13:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T14:04:17.000Z","uid":39886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b4cfea3c38cff2f0ede094155bbd39930b203348","tid":209793,"uid":39886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"巴絲打有冇試過 <br />\n打邊爐既時候 <br />\n食物數量同人數唔成正比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的 <br />\n早排食牛涮X <br />\n4個人 <br />\n但係佢次次都係黎兩碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想問下 <br />\n唔係應該一人一碟既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解會係4個人兩碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定係我可以要求佢再比多兩碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91bf04f750e7247889fb3019e7b6101b7b02fc9","tid":209793,"uid":10441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"任嗌架喎"},{"pid":"676b40c01067bb7a072f7410c52dfcb901f1d8ac","tid":209793,"uid":27821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:06:59.000Z","msg":"任嗌架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8abdbc59bfe2345d9e195c9f9abd201a9ff9f8e","tid":209793,"uid":40490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"嗌一次唔夠 你有無嗌兩次"},{"pid":"6091ce74dfda80ce0f730162f978f772d4915f0e","tid":209793,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"任嗌架喎"},{"pid":"a917cc614a929dbf2c1c9c5ab162db68b1aa5a55","tid":209793,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"任嗌架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6435c87d7bd98778bece80b654eb8c2b43c5ab","tid":209793,"uid":39886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT